---
// Component Imports
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

---

<Layout title="About AdsEngineer - High Performance Tracking Infrastructure">
  <Header />
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-[#0B0B15] text-white">
    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900/20 to-cyan-900/20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700/50">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-2">0ms</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Cold Starts</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">V8 Isolate Performance</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700/50">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">99.9%</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Edge Reliability</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">Global distribution</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700/50">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">EU-Native</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Data Sovereignty</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">GDPR-Compliant Nodes</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700/50">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">~0€</div>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Infra Spend</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">Serverless Efficiency</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission: Digital Sovereignty</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We are building an independent infrastructure layer between European businesses and US Ad-Giants. 
            We don't just fix tracking; we architect digital sovereignty.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert mx-auto">
          <h2>The Engineering Philosophy</h2>
          <p>
            In a world where traditional tracking methods are failing, we realized that the solution wasn't just better marketing—it was better engineering.
            For too long, businesses have relied on heavy, inefficient Docker containers and US-based cloud giants for tracking. These systems were never built for the high-precision requirements of 2026.
          </p>

          <p>
            We founded AdsEngineer with a simple belief: <strong>Infrastructure should be invisible, unblockable, and independent.</strong> By moving away from legacy cloud stacks to edge-native V8 Isolates, we've achieved performance that standard Google Cloud solutions simply cannot match.
          </p>

          <h2>Meet the Architect</h2>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center py-8">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p>
                AdsEngineer was founded by a systems engineer who saw the inherent flaws in "Marketing Tech". While marketers were trying to hack pixels, we were studying V8 engine internals and global edge networking.
              </p>
              <p>
                "I realized that running tracking in Docker containers (Google Cloud Run) was like using a truck to deliver a letter. It's slow, expensive, and prone to cold-start failures. Edge-native V8 Isolates are the surgical instrument needed for modern attribution."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2>Our Technical Roadmap</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 my-12">
            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="text-cyan-400 mt-0">Phase 1: Edge-Native GCLID Preservation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Hardening the foundation with 0ms cold starts and unblockable data persistence on the edge.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="text-purple-400 mt-0">Phase 2: GTM-to-Edge Compiler Expansion</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Supporting complex GTM triggers and custom variables through native Rust-powered compilation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
              <h3 class="text-green-400 mt-0">Phase 3: Multi-Edge Redundancy</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Cross-network edge synchronization between Cloudflare, Fastly, and Vercel for zero-failure infrastructure.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center mt-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900/40 to-cyan-900/40 border border-white/10 p-12 rounded-2xl">
            <h2 class="mt-0">Ready for a Stack Audit?</h2>
            <p class="mb-8">Stop guessing. Let's look at your infrastructure together.</p>
            <a href="https://cal.com/stefan-pirker-nmurov/30min" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-cyan-500 hover:from-cyan-500 hover:to-purple-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl inline-block">
              Audit My Stack
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
